    description: ["Nestled within an exclusive gated community, these lots offer a prime location just 10 minutes from Dominical, 10 minutes from the airport and 20 minutes from the world famous Marina Pez Vela in Quepos, Costa Rica. Conveniently situated off the main coastal highway, accessing these lots is truly effortless!", "The community entrance features stunning landscaped gardens, creating a welcoming atmosphere for residents and visitors alike. With building permits secured, realizing your dream home is both seamless and stress-free—just bring your vision to life!", "Surrounded by lush greenery and a tranquil setting, each lot provides ample space to craft your perfect home, whether it’s a contemporary retreat or a traditional sanctuary.", "Matapalo is renowned for its pristine beaches, vibrant local culture, and proximity to essential amenities, ensuring both relaxation and convenience. This lot is an excellent opportunity to build not only your dream home, but also a smart investment in one of the areas with the greatest growth and appreciation!", "Don’t miss this unique opportunity in one of Costa Rica’s most sought-after locations!", "Contact us today to schedule your private tour and start envisioning the possibilities of luxury living in Matapalo!"],
