    description: ["This 18-acre property is located in Platanillo less than 5 min from the paved road and sits at approx 1000 ft elevation. The property has road frontage on a public road which means that it can be segregated and can be used for commercial or residential purposes. It also has power, legal AYA water, and fiber optic internet.", "The upper building site is huge and has great sunset ocean views. It is big enough for a hotel or a large estate. There is an internal road that winds down through the center of the property and has access to several more building sites. There is a large flat area in the middle of the very buildable property, and then the road ends at another large building site. There is a creek at the bottom of the property too. I’m sure with a little exploration more building sites can be discovered.", "The mix of ocean and mountain views and easy access and all of the infrastructure make this property a great option. Whether you are looking to land bank or develop right away, properties like this are hard to find."],
