    description: ["This 1614 sq. ft. villa is located in a desirable gated community with a premium location overlooking the pool & landscaped gardens. All living spaces have A/C (brand new inverters) and are individually controlled to adjust each room separately. All windows are screened to allow the natural breeze to flow through the unit while keeping the insects out.", "On the main level you enter into the living area with an oversized kitchen area. The large marble island provides ample counter space for gourmet cooking or entertaining family and friends. This kitchen is outfitted with stainless steal appliance: large fridge with ice maker, dishwasher, and new slim counter cooktop. Living area has beautiful views through the large sliding glass door out to the lush pool area. A full bathroom is located on this floor, allowing maximum flexibility with how you live or rent this unit.", "In the upper level of this villa is where the 2 bedrooms are located with a shared full bathroom. The master bedroom features a wrap around balcony that captures a panoramic view of the gardens and masterly design pool.", "While your not enjoying the luxurious feel of the villa, relax outside on your wrap around terrace in one of the main loungers or swing away and ready a book in the hammock. With the pool being only steps away from your villa you will feel like your living in your own resort! Beside the pool is a covered bbq & entertainment area perfect for small get togethers or just cooking outdoors.", "Large outdoor storage areas are available to store your beach equipment, tools and any items you want kept separate from the main living areas.", "Minutes away from the famous Manuel Antonio Espadilla Beach, and National Park and countless fine dining restaurants. The main grocery story is walking distance, which means a car is not necessary for this simple style of living.", "Recently updated furniture; bed sets & sofas along with new cooking pot and pans. This condo comes turn-key ready for a full time resident or vacation rental.", "Monthly HOA: $200"],
