    description: ["Retire Early! Live in 1 Villa and rent the others as short term or long term rentals to pay for your lifestyle and all your expenses!", "Very unique opportunity for anyone looking to live in Paradise and manage their own schedule while collecting rent. This one and half acre property is well located within the gated community of “Finca Se Ve Bien” which is only 3 minutes from Quepos and accessed by a paved road.", "Each of the three homes (two of them with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, and one with one bedroom and one bathroom) are one-level structures with covered terraces and sensible floor plans. The finishes and fixtures are attractive and tastefully done. There aren’t many properties which allow for an owner to live comfortably and collect income with minimal effort, all of which is offered in a preferred setting with new, well-maintained construction and nice supporting infrastructure (fences, gates, landscaping, driveways, retention, gardens, lighting, etc).", "The property and residential development is well-established and home to several full time residences and vacation rental properties, conveniently located 7 minutes to the world renown Marina Pez Vela Marin and just 15 minutes to the iconic Manuel Antonio National Park. The property being offered sits at the end of a private road and is compromised of a tract of rolling hillside land which overlooks the forest and high mountain range in the distance. Three, separate homes are set tastefully on the property, each with their independent access and sense of privacy. The property is only a few years old and has been impeccably maintained by the European owners who built it.", "The gardens are maturing nicely and there is still additional area on the property for further construction if desired.", "Please inquire today about this well-priced opportunity."],
