    description: ["REDUCED FROM $10,080,000 USD", "This is truly an exceptional opportunity for a world-class real estate development in Manuel Antonio, the No.1 most visited area in all of Costa Rica.", "This impressive 84 hectare parcel has expansive views of the sparkling Pacific as far as the eyes can see. Has the original survey marker from 1955, recording this parcel as the highest point in all of Manuel Antonio. Your view will remain undisturbed & unobstructed! Enjoy sunrises over the bordering mountains, and sunsets over the tropical waters.", "This parcel features panoramic ocean views, and lush jungle surroundings with a beautiful river and “El Salto” waterfall , the only waterfall of its kind in the entire area. A developer’s “Dream Property”, zoned for Hotels, Spas, Condominiums, Adventure Parks, Ecotourism, etc. Direct public road access to both the Quepos airport (1km) and the Manuel Antonio National Park and Espadilla Beach. This property is part of the 600 acre, Master Planned, ” L’ Aventura Resort and Spa”, an Adventure Lifestyle Community."],
