    description: ["The Elan at Ballena beach condominiums are the most luxurious condos in Costa Ballena, Costa Rica. Elan is the only development with private direct beach access on a flat easy walking trail through a gorgeous jungle setting. The beach at Playa Ballena is one of the most beautiful in the area and has a Blue Flag designation; which means it is one of the most pristine in all of Costa Rica. The extensive beach area is calm and stable for swimming and water sports for all ages. The Elan community is gated and very safe and secure.", "The condo location was chosen by the owners as one of the first purchases at Elan, meaning they had the opportunity to select one of the most ideal properties possible, tucked away and facing natural jungle surroundings. This spacious home has 2 bedrooms, each with full bathrooms and walk-in closets. There is a half bathroom in the common area as well. The condo has a full living room, dining room, kitchen and a laundry room. There is a large private terrace that can be entered from the dining room and 2nd bedroom where you can enjoy a meal while taking in the view. The master bedroom has a second private terrace where you overlook a beautiful jungle view and can watch the monkeys play while drinking your morning coffee. Luxurious finishes throughout including all Italian tile floors, air conditioners, Quartz counters, Bosch appliances, and fine imported furnishings. The property is just a short walk to the beach, providing quick and easy access to a serene and relaxing setting. The property has a large swimming pool, hot tub and BBQ area as well.", "– Elevator – Parking – 24 Hour Security – Beach Access – Pools – Gardens and Rainforest Views", "The condo is stocked with everything you will need to enjoy during your holiday in paradise. The kitchen is fully equipped with cooking utensils, plates, glasses, silverware, and more. Appliances in the kitchen with a full size refrigerator and freezer, induction cook-top stove/oven, dishwasher, and microwave. All high quality linens and towels are included. High speed WiFi internet can be accessed throughout the suite and development. Cable TV is included in the living room and bedrooms.", "There is also an elevator for those that do not want to use the stairs. Being elevated on the second floor allows guests to be eye level with Howler and White-Face Monkeys, as well as, toucans, parrots, macaws, and more! Enjoy your vacation in style with all the amenities you deserve; while being immersed in nature and beauty of the true Costa Rica experience.", "On-site concierge service can book all your tours such as; zip-lining, surfing lessons, white-water rafting, sport fishing, whale and dolphin tours, snorkeling or diving expeditions, bird-watching, hiking tours, mangrove kayaking, Corcovado National Park or Manuel Antonio National Park day trips, and much more! We can also assist with car rentals, travel plans, shuttle buses, commuter flights, or anything else that will make your vacation a stress free and effortless experience."],
    features: ["Condominium with security", "Furnished", "Controlled Access", "Swimming Pool", "Balcony", "Security Guard", "Open Design", "Jacuzzi", "Exclusive Community", "Landscaped Gardens", "Private Water Source", "Pets Allowed", "Storage Area"],
