    description: ["Reduced from $1.6 Million", "This is a unique opportunity to invest in a boutique hotel in Manuel Antonio with property that has 10 condo residences complete plus a managers home that all have individual title, electric and water meters. This hotel has its own front reception area along with a restaurant and bar with all its licences and permits up to date. This whole property has been built around the landscape grounds with a large pool as the centerpiece.", "The restaurant has been set up that it can be a part of the hotel or can be contracted out and rented to one of the many restauranteurs of Manuel Antonio. Focusing on creating delicious meals using local and Tico ingredients while providing their guests with all their comfort foods. There is no better place to relax than the bar where you can enjoy all the tropical drinks and local beers pool side while being steps away from your condo.", "This hotel is set in an ideal location where you are away from the busy road, yet 150 meters away from public transportations. For visitors traveling through Costa Rica visiting all the highlight destinations, this is one that doesn’t not require a 4×4 vehicle making it more accessible and friendly for first time travelers while plenty of parking available.", "This represents and opportunity for someone who would like to take over a hotel and run it as their own business, or for an investor looking to flip for re-sale. With limited amount of inventory available in Manuel Antonio, you could sell re-sell each condo residence individual and earn a profitable gain.", "All offers are considered and presented to owner!"],
