    description: ["This luxurious, contemporary home in the heart of Manuel Antonio, is near one of the most famous beaches in Costa Rica. This home works beautifully as a family home, a time-share, or vacation rental as it can sleep as many as 14. The main house has 2 master bedrooms with king-size beds fitted with luxury linens and en suite bathrooms. It boasts a full-service kitchen with high-end stainless steel appliances and all you need to cook a great meal! The living room is spacious and opens up to a terrace for maximum relaxation. The villa also has a loft area to hang out and play games and sleep an additional 2 people on a pullout sofa, if needed.", "The home also has 4 self-contained rentals – 3 individual units have their own separate entrances with all the amenities – kitchen, living room, balcony, bedroom, and bathroom. The studio also has its own kitchen bedroom, patio, and bathroom. The layout of this property is unique and allows couples to have privacy or to share each other’s company in the common areas throughout the main house.", "Located one-minute walk to the bus stop and access to transportation that will take you to the beach or the town of Quepos in either direction — each less than 10 minutes ride in either direction – this home is nevertheless surrounded by an envelope of jungle for utmost privacy. The home also has a great swimming pool with a gazebo hangout area. The outdoor common area is equipped with a grill and patio furniture for relaxing. Enjoy all the animals that visit – monkeys, toucans, etc.", "The property is a vacation rental home and typically rents: 6 bedrooms – $750/night or $4,500/week 5 bedrooms – $650/night or 4,200/week 4 bedrooms – $550/night or $4,000/week"],
