    description: ["This is a solid concrete construction home with a total of 3 bedrooms & 3.5 bathrooms along with an completely enclosed yard with two electronic gates. This home is located in a residential neighborhood with a combination of local & foreigner neighbors. The hummingbirds and butterflies are frequent visitors along with the green parrots which fly by daily first thing in the morning and just before sunset.", "This villa has a electronic gate that opens up into a car port area with brick pavers and space for 2 vehicles. You can enter through the house through the main front door, or through a patio door from the car port that leads you into the kitchen & dining area. The common area of this home is open and perfect for entertaining with multiple seating areas indoors and outdoors. The entire home has A/C which makes it perfect for you and your family or your Airbnb guests.", "The master bedroom features an outdoor patio area along with a walk in closet and ensuite bathroom (all showers feature rain shower heads). The second bedroom is off the main living area along with the second full bathroom. Additionally there is a in-law suite which is accessed from the back patio area which leads to another spacious bedroom with ensuite bathroom. This could also be used as your office space, craft room, helpers suite, or just another bedroom! This is a property of convenience especially with the single level floor plan!", "There is an additional electronic gate that leads to the adjacent side of the house which the current owner uses the 7m x 7m covered patio area with 7 m high ceilings for additional parking for his private shuttle business. This area is perfect for storing vehicles, dry boat storage or outdoor entertainment area. There is an outdoor wash area and half bathroom connected to it. The house also has an additional external locked storage area with a back up water tank and a laundry area!", "There is a high demand for long term rentals due to the lack of inventory which makes this property so desirable for someone looking to earn passive income. Its location makes it a property of convenience as you are only minutes to everything ie:"],
