    description: ["Casa Española truly is magnificent. Arranged over 4 floors, our villa provides privacy and comfort to both large and small groups alike. With 8 lavish bedroom suites, 8 bathrooms, 5 ocean view balconies, 4 separate living areas, dining areas and kitchens, a private pool, a waterfall Jacuzzi, a hot tub and air conditioning throughout, we can comfortably accommodate up to 30+ people (more if your party includes small children). This is an incredible vacation rental profits with great rental earnings.", "Situated in the heart of Manuel Antonio, within walking distance to excellent restaurants and bars, this spectacular home offers high quality, adaptable accommodation with spectacular ocean views from every room. Generous outdoor living spaces ensure your connection with the amazing natural surroundings.", "This luxury Mediterranean inspired home is flooded with natural light. Floor-to-ceiling glass doors / windows and adjoining patios from all living and bedroom areas gives truly spectacular views from every direction. So lay back, relax and watch the boats sail across the Pacific Ocean as the birds soar across clear blue sky.", "A large sun deck by the pool is perfect for lounging the days away in the gorgeous warmth from the tropical sun. The outdoor entertaining area includes a super sized BBQ grill that makes for easy entertaining of your family and friends.", "As the property is nestled in the jungle, you can also expect daily visitors of squirrel, titi, white faced or howler monkeys, sloths, lizards, iguanas, birds, butterflies and other exotic wildlife. It’s so beautiful here the danger is you’ll never want to leave!", "Casa Española is built on a titled lot of 929 M2. The sale includes the neighboring titled lot of 826 M2 which can used for additional privacy or for additional vacation rental home!"],
