    description: ["Casa Iconic features the main house with 2 additional guest houses that can be accessed within the property or entered into separately. This modern home offers 10,000 Sq.Ff of living space with a state of the art infinity pool with a glass edge overlooking the ocean and a 20 ft cascade waterfall to the lower level pool. Located in the prestigious and multi-million dollar gated community of Costa Verde with private gym, tennis courts, pavilion and helipad.", "Main house: The main house features the beautiful custom kitchen with open terrace and outdoor kitchen along with 1 master bedroom on the main level. This master bedroom is uniquely different from the other master suites as it has a custom bathtub with panoramic views. This level has infinity edge pool along with a separate hot tub/spa, the ideal spot to enjoy the evening with the cool evening mountain temperatures; additionally there is a indoor and outdoor fireplace that can be enjoyed! As you go upstairs to the upper level you have free floating wooden stairs accessing the upper 2 master bedroom suites with ocean views that will make your jaw drop again!", "Level 1 • Guest House: You can access this guest home with via a private driveway or from a stair way that connects to the main house. This villa features 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom with custom showers, full kitchenette , living room and private dipping pool. This villa has it own wifi and power so it can be independent from the main house.", "Upper Level • Studio House: This studio is accessed through a breeze way going to the upper level off the main house. This studio features 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom with an indoor and outdoor shower, full kitchenette, living room and the most iconic view in the entire property.", "Price Increase on January 2023 at $3.1M Projected Completion: August 2023"],
