    description: ["Welcome to Casa Ultimo Sueño, the ultimate luxurious oasis located above the picturesque coastal town of Uvita, Costa Rica. This stunning estate is perched on the front ridge facing the prime attraction, “Whale’s Tail” beach, and boasts the best views of this iconic Costa Rican landmark.", "No expense was spared in creating a masterpiece that seamlessly blends the lush natural surroundings with world-class luxury. From the moment you arrive, you will appreciate the quality of construction and the attention to detail in every aspect of this property.", "Casa Ultimo Sueño features a main home with 4 bedrooms on 2 levels and a separate Entertainment House on an adjoining lot with an additional 2 bedrooms. The open-concept design of the interior spaces provides an optimal layout for entertaining and incorporates the tropical rainforest seamlessly. The rich finishes and stunning craftsmanship in every room draw your attention to the incredible views that have been carefully opened throughout.", "The exterior spaces of this ocean-view estate are equally impressive, with rich tropical landscaping highlighting the natural beauty of Costa Rica. The custom pool area is an absolute showstopper, offering a custom jacuzzi with a waterfall feature, a wet bar, and an entertainment area, that gives a sensational spa-like retreat that is perfect for large gatherings or intimate get-togethers.", "This world-class estate is perfect for even the most discerning buyers, and the location has been carefully selected to provide privacy and convenience. The prime views of “Whale’s Tail” beach and some of the most dramatic sunsets on the pacific coast are just a few of the many features that make Casa Ultimo Sueño a true paradise.", "If you’re looking for the ultimate luxurious oasis in Costa Rica, look no further than Casa Ultimo Sueño."],
