    description: ["This brand new home in upscale Escalares comes with what everyone is looking for; privacy, ocean views, jungle setting, creek, high-speed internet, close to amenities, and tons of space to build or plant your gardens. You will love the feel of this home as you are floating over the treetop looking out toward the ocean. You are only 5 minutes from the coastal highway on a well-maintained road and less than 5 minutes from Scala restaurant and a health food store.", "An excellent reputable builder built this home as his personal home and you will see the attention to detail as soon as you walk in the front door! Enjoy the natural coralina tile below your feet as you take a swim in your saltwater pool! Naturally cool with amazing airflow, there is always a breeze, ceiling fans throughout the house, and high-efficiency air conditioners. Water treatment plant so that you can use your wastewater for irrigation and solar hot water with a high-efficiency variable pool pump to keep your monthly bills down.", "Custom wood doors, windows, cabinets, decks-teak, hardwood cinezaro, laurel, and cedar are found throughout the house. The roof consists of 4 layers for insulation and soundproof consisting of a beautiful wood ceiling, 3″ of insulation, metal subroof, and natural clay tile with great overhangs for shade and hang-out areas!", "There is also an opportunity to purchase a 3 bedroom guest house which is currently on this property for $425k and earn passive income.", "Please inquire now with any questions!"],
