    description: ["Welcome to luxury living at the prestigious Escalares Village, an exclusive gated community located in the heart of Escalares. Boasting a plethora of first-class amenities, this upscale community has everything you need to live and enjoy the best.", "Indulge in healthy living at Alexa’s health food store and unwind at the luxurious Scala restaurant and spa. Stay in shape at the fitness center or socialize with friends and neighbors at the homeowners’ clubhouse. Experience the lush beauty of the jungle on the community’s hiking trails or enjoy a game of basketball in the midst of nature on the community’s private court.", "With legal ASADA water and soil studies, ensure that your dream home can be built with ease. You will have access to top builder Leif Bernhardt, who has created and built all of the homes in this remarkable community.", "This prime location is ideally situated just minutes away from the pristine beaches of Dominical and Uvita. Revel in the breathtaking ocean views that overlook a 15-acre private reserve while taking in the sunset from the comfort of your own poolside. The sounds of the crashing waves below will lull you to sleep at night as you take in the serene tree-top views of the jungle where you can spot toucans and monkeys playing.", "This is the last remaining lot available in Escalares Village, and it is perfect for a vacation rental home or you’re forever home. Don’t miss the opportunity to become a part of this exceptional community and build your dream home in paradise. Live your best life at Escalares Village."],
