    description: ["Casa Ola Vista is a stunning single-level, luxury 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom beach home featuring a front-row seat, looking over Dominicalito Bay and the sprawling Pacific Ocean all the way down the coast toward Manuel Antonio. The house was designed to make this amazing ocean view, the focal point and views are seen from each bedroom and the living areas. The incredible views, coupled with the attention to detail, define the property as a peerless luxury vacation rental in the Dominical area. Casa Ola Vista is the perfect place to base your adventures, watch wildlife, sip cocktails, and grill up fresh dinners. It is located less than one minute off the main road and, though it is situated only one minute to Playa Dominicalito, 5-minutes to Playa Dominical, and 15-minutes to Uvita, you’ll feel a million miles away.", "The heart of the home is a great room that includes a gourmet kitchen that will allow you to prepare your favorite meals using the local fresh produce and fruits. Hire a private chef to cater your meals or use our concierge service to stock the kitchen with your favorite foods and beverages. The center island in the kitchen is accompanied by a drink bar that boasts a Vitamix blender and ice machine to use as you master the perfect fresh fruit smoothie or exotic cocktail. The mini-fridge is perfectly situated for guests to grab a cold beer or wine refill. The kitchen spills into a large living room that completely opens up to a 2000 sq. foot fully covered terrace with an infinity-edge saltwater pool that beckons to be enjoyed. You will spend hours enjoying this outside living space, the way most of the locals spend their time.", "Casa Ola Vista is perfect for 4 couples or 3 families with a separate bedroom for the children. The northern wing of the house has a large master ocean view suite with a king-size bed and a jungle view bedroom with a large king-size bed and a small loft-style twin. The southern wing of the home has a laundry room and two spacious ocean-view suites, both with king-size beds. With dense rainforest directly below and bordering the north side of the property, the sights and sounds of pure Costa Rica will completely envelop you. You can listen to Howler Monkeys in the distance, watch white-face monkeys leaping through the trees and witness colorful Toucans flying through the air. Casa Ola Vista is set back off the main road via a long driveway with an electronically controlled gate. With A/C in every bedroom, and high-speed fiber-optic internet.", "Enquire now as the views and location do not get any better than this!!!"],
