    description: ["This brand new model home is located in the new master-planned community of Jardines Del Sol, in the heart of Uvita. This convenient location makes this home extremely attractive, with easy access to schools, restaurants, bars and entertainment, as well as grocery stores, banks, pharmacy and doctors offices. Take a leisurely stroll to the farmers market, or spend time riding your bike along the newly paved road. This home is priced extremely aggressively and is expected to sell fast.", "This home is impressive from the moment you arrive, with modern lines, vaulted roof lines, and a gorgeous tiled feature wall that continues from the front of the house, to the rear. The impressive entry door is custom made, and the concrete driveway gives you access to this impressive entry, and to the secondary laundry room access. From the moment you open the door, you will be enticed with the natural light that permeates in every room, the stunning furnishings, and the modern chef’s kitchen.", "The kitchen was finished with exquisite high designer cabinets to make it both. beautiful and functional, with high end appliances including a gas range, a high quality refrigerator, and a convenient dishwasher. Other appliances include the washer and dryer, located in the separate laundry room.", "The main part of the home is completely open, with a spaciously appointed dining area, living room, and a walk-out patio around the concrete and tile pool. The dining room is impressive, with an amazing dining table and chairs hand selected to give the area a modern yet tropical feel. The living area is generous in size, and can accommodate your family and friends.", "This home has two master suites, each with a lovely ensuite. The bathrooms boast double vanity sinks, and large walk-in showers. There is also an addition half bath for convenience and privacy.", "The inside living spaces flow seamlessly to the rear patio and covered living area. Here you will find plenty of room to set up your grill and your patio furniture. The pool is inviting and the perfect place to cool off after an exciting day.", "Did we mention that the location of this home is ideal? Leave your car behind and take an enjoyable walk, or ride your bike to town… Your best life awaits!"],
