    description: ["Suenos Pacificos Front Row Ocean View Luxury Villa in the Prestigious Las Olas of Dominical", "Discover what it means to live in the lap of luxury at Suenos Pacificos (Pacific Dreams), which is now available on the Dominical luxury real estate market for the first time ever. As soon as you step foot onto the property, you will be stunned by the beautiful tropical setting and well-made architectural features that make this a work of art. These characteristics include the clay barrel tiled roof, the beautiful wood, and iron trim, and the decorative floor tiles that exhibit Spanish Colonial flair.", "This property, which is in the prestigious neighborhood of Las Olas, is thought to have the best location, view, and level of safety along the South Pacific Coast of Costa Rica. You and your guests need not worry about security, as this property is safely guarded around the clock with controlled gated access and 24-hour security guard service. You can easily get to the Coastal Highway, tours, and shopping in the area because the property is just 500 meters from Dominicalito Beach and between the towns of Dominical and Uvita.", "Completed in 2006, this one-story home has a total of 4,000 square feet of construction space and is situated on a sprawling 1.24-acre property. The home offers 3 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a sizable pool, perfect for outdoor entertaining. It is a great place to work thanks to the dedicated office space and the fiber optic internet that is hard-wired into the building. Additionally, the detached garage and storage room offer safe parking for your vehicles.", "From the infinity edge pool take in the amazing panoramic ocean views stretching from Punta Dominical up the coast to Manuel Antonio National Park. The well-kept lawn and gardens have a wide range of native plants and animals, making it a great place to relax and take it easy. The jungle around the property is full of animals like Congo monkeys, White-faced monkeys, Chachalacas, and more.", "This Home Will Produce an Excellent Return as an Income Producing Vacation Rental", "This home located in the exclusive Las Olas enclave offers a one-of-a-kind chance to own front-row property in Dominical’s most exclusive beachside neighborhood. Due to the community’s walk to the beach location, ease of access, and close proximity to the region’s most popular tourist attractions, it is not a surprise that neighboring homes; in Las Olas are consistently booked before other options that are located further up the mountain. Simply put, Las Olas is the best location to own a luxury vacation rental home in the Dominical area.", "If you are a serious luxury home buyer who wants a top-notch vacation rental home that is easy to get to, this estate property has everything you need. Do not pass up the opportunity of a lifetime to acquire the pinnacle of luxury real estate on the southern Pacific coast of Costa Rica."],
