    description: ["Enjoy the newest property available in Manuel Antonio! “Utopia” – an imagined place or state of things in which everything is perfect.", "Utopia offers 7 vacation rentals in the most renowned and desired area of Manuel Antonio with an unbeatable location and ocean views. Located beside Tulemar Resort – Rated No.1 Resort in the World by Trip Advisor.", "Each of the rentals feature comfortable beds & linens with artistic finishes and Costa Rican flares – each with private bathrooms and large balconies/terraces to enjoy the surrounding views. One of the rental spaces is a full apartment which could be used as the owner’s residence or a deluxe rental.", "Rentals: The property is managed by VACASA, the fastest growing vacation rental group in Costa Rica which offers the current owner guaranteed passive income with zero involvement. Utopia will flourish in the rental market and is targeted to cater to the middle class rentals specializing in large traveling groups accommodating up to 16. The rental management program is turn-key and allows owners without rental experience to earn easy rental income.", "Development: Utopia offers 1,086 M2 of land with 3,507 SF of covered living areas with the capability of building multiple levels above the road as the neighboring properties have done. The property is ready with Electricity and Water which makes going vertical easy and fast compared to buying land with utilities.", "Investment: The market of Manuel Antonio has limited inventory (properties) with a growing demand. Contact us now to speak with our investment team and learn how to diversify your portfolio to secure your income with solid asset that you can visit and enjoy!", "Highlights:"],
