    description: ["This is the best value property in Manuel Antonio and located off the main drive which means you are just mins away to everything i.e. restaurants, bars, the beach; many of which are within walking distance.", "There are a total of 12 condos within the Titi Condo Development distributed between two buildings and two levels. This unit has a single level distribution and is located pool side! There is a shared BBQ area and outdoor patio furniture for all residents to enjoy. It is very common to see macaws and monkeys, as they pass by daily!", "As you enter the unit, you enter into an open design kitchen and living area! The kitchen features solid wood cabinetry and black granite countertops. There are two bedrooms equal in size, each with sliding patio doors that go into your own backyard space that can be personalized as you desire. Each bedroom has its own built-in closet, and their own a/c unit. The bathroom is located in between the bedrooms and accessed from the main living area.", "This unit is perfect for those who want to be close to everything and be in a community with neighbors. Having a vehicle is not necessary as you are steps away from the main road where the public bus passes by every 30 mins that goes to the beach and to town. This is the perfect home for a first-time buyer or for an investor looking to own another property in a the booming and appreciating town of Manuel Antonio. It is nearly impossible to find a 2-bedroom villa at this price point.", "Condo Fees: $200 per month which includes the pool cleaning & maintenance, landscaping, cleaning and maintenance of common areas, the water for each villa & shared areas and maintenance to the external areas of the buildings.", "This is a property that will not last!"],
